OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1782411505
OL,3,CMan dies after being restrained on
OL,4,Cflight to Manchester Airport
OL,6,FAn investigation is under way after
OL,7,Fthe death of a man who was restrained
OL,8,Fon a flight from Cyprus to the UK.
OL,10,FCallum Kerr, 35, was restrained by
OL,11,Fpassengers and crew on the flight from
OL,12,FLarnaca to Manchester, a spokesman for
OL,13,FGreater Manchester Police (GMP) said.
OL,15,FThe force said officers were called at
OL,16,Fabout 2.25am on 22 June to reports of
OL,17,Fa man behaving aggressively on the
OL,18,Fflight and assaulting a passenger and
OL,19,Fmember of cabin crew.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
