FL,365,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1782411505
OL,3,CMan dies after being restrained on
OL,4,Cflight to Manchester Airport
OL,6,FThe spokesman said: "Officers boarded
OL,7,Fthe aircraft on its arrival and
OL,8,Flocated the man, who was being
OL,9,Frestrained by passengers and aircrew
OL,10,Fat the rear of the plane.
OL,12,F"Officers used handcuffs to detain him
OL,13,Fand quickly identified he was
OL,14,Funresponsive, through the provision of
OL,15,Ffirst aid, and began with CPR."
OL,17,FMr Kerr died in hospital a day later,
OL,18,Fpolice said.
OL,26,@nD@UOUtD@AOUwD@_O]
