FL,365,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1782411505
OL,3,CMan dies after being restrained on
OL,4,Cflight to Manchester Airport
OL,6,FIn a statement, his family said:
OL,7,F"Callum was a family man, father to
OL,8,Fthree beautiful young children, a
OL,9,Flover of sport and with a heart of
OL,10,Fgold."
OL,12,FA mandatory referral to the
OL,13,FIndependent Office for Police Conduct
OL,14,F(IOPC) was made by the force because
OL,15,Fof police contact with Mr Kerr before
OL,16,Fhis death.
OL,18,FDetectives from GMP are investigating
OL,19,Fcircumstances on the flight before the
OL,20,Farrival of officers.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
