FL,365,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1782411505
OL,3,CMan dies after being restrained on
OL,4,Cflight to Manchester Airport
OL,6,FChief Superintendent Mike Allen said:
OL,7,F"I know there were many people on the
OL,8,Fflight who witnessed the violence and
OL,9,Fdisruption prior to officers' arrival.
OL,11,F"We know passengers and aircrew worked
OL,12,Fto detain the man to bring the
OL,13,Fincident to an end.
OL,15,F"Our detectives are investigating this
OL,16,Fto understand the full circumstances."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUwD@AOUxD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
