FL,365,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1782411505
OL,3,CMan dies after being restrained on
OL,4,Cflight to Manchester Airport
OL,6,FIOPC director of engagement Amanda
OL,7,FRowe said evidence, including body-
OL,8,Fworn footage, had been reviewed and
OL,9,Fpolice officers were being treated as
OL,10,Fwitnesses, rather than being
OL,11,Finvestigated for their conduct.
OL,13,FShe said: "I want to reassure people
OL,14,Four investigation will be thorough,
OL,15,Fand independent of the police, to
OL,16,Fensure we understand exactly what has
OL,17,Fhappened."
OL,26,@uD@KOU
